-----BEGIN PUBLIC KEY-----
PLACEHOLDER
This file should be replaced with the actual public half of the
cosign keypair generated for the project. Generate with:

  cosign generate-key-pair

The private half goes into the GitHub repo secrets as COSIGN_PRIVATE_KEY;
the password as COSIGN_PASSWORD. CI uses keyless OIDC by default so
this file is only needed for offline verification.
-----END PUBLIC KEY-----
